divs: Sighting Details We were fishing on mountain lake one evening early 1990s and when it got dark we looked around the lake and noticed what we thought was a round house.The lights coming from the object were different though greenish and what looked like a television had a beam of light coming out of it that just stopped inside.We did see people with large heads and long arms,only shadowish though.We watched in amazement as we realized they coudlnt have built a round house there in two weeks as we went fishing there almost every weekend.About 2:00am we both had a fish on and hadnt caught anything all night,at which point it was gone.There was a time lapse of app. 2 hours that we do not know what happeneed.I am wondering if it is possible to be hypnotized for the purpose of trying to remember what exactly happened that very strange night.Oh there is no house there.
